title: David Dobrik Lights His Friend On Fire & Ethan Squashes Another Beef - Off The Rails #46
description: Today is an odyssey of an episode! We squash TWO beefs, one with Bradley Martyn and one with a surprise call with Jidion. We also discuss Ethan's biggest hater, try and guess which parent belongs to which crew member in the Families Photo Game, and much more!
